    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And German because it's our neighbor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Nobody like learn Russian, because Russian was something what nobody like.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I learn German.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And before you have the diploma, high school diploma, you must speak good other language.",
