    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I was looking for some job where German language is required.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I found something that was in Warsaw-- company from Berlin who-- I think so, before the war the-- the company was a transport company like, you know, a company who pack everything and send in the boxes or something like this.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
